@startuml AI_Resume_Builder_Data_Flow_Simplified
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title AI Resume Builder - Simplified Data Flow

actor User
participant "React\nFrontend" as Frontend
participant "Spring Boot\nBackend" as Backend
participant "Gemini AI" as AI
participant "LaTeX\nEngine" as LaTeX
database "Templates" as Templates

== 1. Generate Resume ==

User -> Frontend: Enter description\n+ Select template
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/resume/generate
Backend -> AI: Send prompt
AI --> Backend: Return JSON data
Backend --> Frontend: Resume data
Frontend --> User: Display resume

== 2. Generate LaTeX ==

User -> Frontend: Click "View LaTeX"
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/latex/generate
Backend -> Templates: Load template
Templates --> Backend: Template file
Backend -> Backend: Fill template\n+ Format sections\n+ Ensure 3 points/project
Backend --> Frontend: LaTeX code
Frontend --> User: Show in editor

== 3. Compile PDF ==

User -> Frontend: Click "Compile"
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/latex/compile
Backend -> LaTeX: Run pdflatex
LaTeX --> Backend: PDF bytes
Backend --> Frontend: PDF file
Frontend --> User: Display PDF

== 4. Download ==

User -> Frontend: Click "Download"
Frontend --> User: Save PDF

note over Backend
**Key Features:**
• Multi-layer validation
• Template-specific formatting
• Auto-generate fallback content
• Error handling at each step
end note

@enduml
